-- BP Completes Installation of New Sealing Cap on Well Spilling Oil in Gulf
-- Vivek Shankar
-- 2010-07-13T00:56:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/bp-completes-installation-of-new-sealing-cap-on-well-spilling-oil-in-gulf.html

          
          
             BP Plc said it completed the
installation of the new sealing cap on the well spilling oil in
the Gulf of Mexico, according to an e-mailed statment.  
          
          


  


        